> [ 2008.237288] Pid: 30, comm: pdflush Not tainted
> 2.6.28-g14-rfkill-nophy-ledon-07485-g9e42d0c #62
> [ 2008.237294] Call Trace:
> [ 2008.237303]  [<c04d7576>] schedule+0x326/0x8e0
